The '''Owners' League''' was a group affiliated with [[Black Sun/Legends|Black Sun]]. When [[Mayli Weng]] came to [[Xizor/Legends|Xizor]] asking for general pay increases and better working environments for the workers of the [[Exotic Entertainers' Union]], Xizor agreed knowing happier employees ment happier customers that resulted in more money being made.

